imdb.plot outline: Six gym instructors have been selected as finalists to become America's most fabulous fitness instructor and win their own reality TV show. Each week they are brought together to go through a series of challenges and competitions and at the end of the series they realise the entire competition is becoming the reality show and the world will see the ugly and competitive truth.
